      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-navy text-[22px] mb-3">What we collect</h2>
      <p>When you submit our quote or contact form, we collect the information you provide: your name, phone number, email address, home address and details about your home (e.g. size, type of cleaning requested, preferred date, notes).</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-navy text-[22px] mb-3">How we use it</h2>
      <p>We use your submission to prepare a quote, answer your question, and schedule service if you choose to book with us. We do not sell your information.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-navy text-[22px] mb-3">Who we share it with</h2>
      <p>Your request may be shared with a vetted local cleaning partner in order to fulfill the service you've requested. We only share what's needed to provide your quote or complete your booking.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-navy text-[22px] mb-3">How long we keep it</h2>
      <p>We keep submission details for as long as needed to respond to your request and, if you become a client, for the duration of our working relationship and a reasonable period afterward for record-keeping.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
